{"tid":1351302,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"你班Hi仔驚到咁","createTime":"2019-07-22T15:06:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-22T16:40:19.000Z","uid":258400,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"c9c999b99b43c252223e6cf04e1e0b4b0fc1f2f1","tid":1351302,"uid":258400,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T15:06:44.000Z","msg":"唔好意思，我唔係想寸你地入嚟...<br />\n但我見到熱門淨係講刀手幾時蒲頭，<br />\n感覺有D浪費依家既時勢!<br />\n<br />\n趁依家香港人俾恐怖氛圍瀧罩緊，<br />\n個個唔敢出街，我地應該加大文宣力度，<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">叫所有人團結三罷</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n我地要有行動，要話俾所有人知，<br />\n尋日唔止得<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">元朗恐襲!</span></strong></span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">仲有上環黑警亂尻開槍</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">仲有警黑勾結</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">仲有港鐵出賣港人</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n我地應該要有即時回應!!!<br />\n我地唔應該令義士既犧牲白費!!!<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88dcca15711d538adf6e9034c2bab0ee2983eeb2","tid":1351302,"uid":258400,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T15:11:00.000Z","msg":"有無人幫幫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f70fcb8caa7a587e3901156204fcecc68a4c8ba","tid":1351302,"uid":110332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T15:13:01.000Z","msg":"香港人衰在過得太安逸，or太容易知足，係人權方面"},{"pid":"e425d96dd6701c0939a68e8652aeb05a40853794","tid":1351302,"uid":258400,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0f70fcb8caa7a587e3901156204fcecc68a4c8ba","tid":1351302,"